OL,3,CArrests made following multiple arson
OL,4,Cattacks in Swansea and Port Talbot
OL,6,FArrests have been made following a
OL,7,Fnumber of arson incidents in the Neath
OL,8,FPort Talbot and Swansea areas.
OL,10,FSouth Wales Police said "four young
OL,11,Fboys" have been arrested over separate
OL,12,Farson incidents in the Port Talbot
OL,13,Farea in the last three weeks.
OL,15,FIt comes as the force released a joint
OL,16,Fstatement with Mid and West Wales Fire
OL,17,Fand Rescue Service (MAWWFRS) following
OL,18,Fa number of recent incidents of arson
OL,19,Fin the area.
