OL,3,CArrests made following multiple arson
OL,4,Cattacks in Swansea and Port Talbot
OL,6,FMAWWFRS said it had recently been
OL,7,F"exceptionally busy" in responding to
OL,8,Flarge-scale wildfires, with a number
OL,9,Fof these incidents started
OL,10,Fdeliberately.
OL,12,FScott O'Kelly, head of arson reduction
OL,13,Fand a station manager, said:
OL,14,F"Unfortunately, MAWWFRS has recently
OL,15,Fresponded to a series of arson-related
OL,16,Fincidents, which range from wildfires
OL,17,Fto fires within derelict properties.
