OL,3,CArrests made following multiple arson
OL,4,Cattacks in Swansea and Port Talbot
OL,6,F"We are continuing to work with
OL,7,Fresidents and partners within the
OL,8,Fcommunities we serve to raise
OL,9,Fawareness of the consequences of arson
OL,10,Fand limit the devastating impact of
OL,11,Fdeliberate fires."
OL,13,FInspector Jared Easton, of South Wales
OL,14,FPolice, added: "Setting fires is
OL,15,Fdangerous and against the law. Four
OL,16,Fyoung boys have been arrested for
OL,17,Fseparate arsons in the Port Talbot
OL,18,Farea in the last three weeks. We will
OL,19,Fnot tolerate this behaviour and will
OL,20,Fdeal robustly with people committing
OL,21,Fthese offences."
